{"tid":1984130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民同意延長限聚令　有市民指影響生活失去基本娛樂","createTime":"2020-04-22T09:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T10:18:51.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44f8df8ea56bb5ee6ccf6511d1fee411685e34c3","tid":1984130,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"政府宣布延長限聚令兩星期至5月7日。<br />\n<br />\n市民張小姐認為本港感染人數少，全因有限聚令，認為延長限聚令對大眾有好處，可以減低疫情散播的機會。<br />\n<br />\n市民陳先生表示，如28日內都沒有新症才代表疫情過去，現時仍未達到，因此同意要延長限聚令。他又說，實施限聚令後，外出的人減少，而減少人群接觸，有助減低傳染機會，認為限聚令有作用。<br />\n<br />\n另一名市民余先生認為，沒有必要延長限聚令，認為影響市民生活，外出吃飯不方便，亦失去基本娛樂。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521856-20200421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521856-20200421.htm&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=3344ef81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521856-20200421.htm&h=3cb6df82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521856-20200421.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n張小姐，延長限聚令可以減低疫情散播的機會，並唔代表要不停延長架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳生，28日內沒有新症基本上唔可能做到，所以依你的想法限聚令應該要不停延長，直至經濟大蕭條到來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n余生的想法我就支持喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cfb23a29fcf11d9361393f61d303fdf3de0df9","tid":1984130,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"tvb咪基本娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de37529fe14fd6852abdc560a4c29908e9de24d0","tid":1984130,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"影響基本娛樂的同時，更影響基本權利<br />\n例如，噚晚元朗天橋告票老屈罰錢"},{"pid":"46e9360d9b973615b0e5dfcd5ed257919e0072b6","tid":1984130,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=e1d6b731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a82252b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n&quot;現時本港大約有5%的患者需入住深切治療部，但當年沙士有四分一患者需深切治療部&quot;<br />\n&quot;現時很多仍然留院的病人都很精神，毋須利用儀器供氧，甚至可以在病房玩電話或做運動，只是等待病毒檢測呈陰性反應&quot;<br />\n&quot;病人失去味覺和嗅覺的情況都很短暫，亦只有少部分病人有肺部纖維化情況&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都話左疫情被誇大啦</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}